00:44:35.383 --> 00:44:37.421
Abigail Porter.

00:44:43.623 --> 00:44:47.298
<i>Sigurni testovi za trudnoću.

00:44:47.352 --> 00:44:49.764
<i>Oni predstavljaju malu revoluciju za

